<title>Exhortation to Praise Christ ƲIT43</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chisʋs ʋt pi̱ nukha̱klo hosh,
 Ant illi tok oke:
 I̱ yimmi achukma mak osh
 E holitoblashke.

[V2]
 Chisʋs ʋt hina hanta ka
 Pim ikbi tok oke;
 Il iakaiya he mak o̱,
 Aiahni tok oke.

[V3]
 Illoh im antihi̱yakmʋt,
 Nana achukma ka
 E pilhi̱sa hinla hokʋt,
 Il aiokpanchishke.

[V4]
 Pi̱ki ʋba binili hosh
 Hʋpibki tok mak o̱,
 Il itʋnoho̱wa hokʋt,
 E holitoblashke.

[V5]
 Eho holitobli hokma,
 Hʋp ikbi tok okʋt,
 Chu̱kʋsh achukma fehna ka
 Et pima hinlʋshke.</lyrics>
<aka>Chisʋs ʋt pi̱ nukha̱klo ho</aka>
<hymn_number>43</hymn_number>
<author>E. M. Bartlett</author>
</song>